Page_0: "I was seated in the mahogany hall when I chanced did see an amazing creature!  Light brown wavy hair, shining blue eyes, and skin of such delicate pink complexion silk would be vulgar if it were held against it.  She was only there for an instant though before she vanished into her chamber, the bolt of the lock falling like a hammer.  Next time you're dusting in the mahogany hall, keep your eyes open.  I'm telling you, she's magnificent!"